
CMakeFiles README

CMakeFiles is a set of CMake files, with a bias towards projects using Fortran.
Homepage: http://cmakefiles.sourceforge.net


Contents:

CMake/		This directory contains CMake modules like compiler options and an example file list.
		Put these files in the CMake/ subdirectory of the main project directory.

CMakeLists/	This directory contains example CMakeLists.txt files.
		Put one of these files in the main project directory.

FindLibs/	This directory contains FindLib.cmake files.  All files use CMakeLocations.cmake, which
		is designed for Linux/Unix/BSD/MacOS.  Put these files in the CMake/ subdirectory of the 
		main project directory.





